arguments.value: Please fund proxy with more than 1 dollars worth of TSRY

documentation.text: @dev Gets price from oracle for GT (i.e., Aave/dollars).

addAllowedTokens(address,address).details: Adds allowed tokens to mapping as well as its corresponding priceFeed.

constructor.details: Constructor - (N.B. Will likely change a lot during development)

params._proxyFactory: : address - The address of the proxy factory (needed for transfering tokens)
params._treasuryTokenAddress: : address - The address of the treasury token
params._voteProxyRegistry: : address- The address of the vote proxy registry                                      (needed for the fund proxy function)

fundProxy(uint256,address,address,uint25.details: Transfer GT to a proxy by first converting TSRY amount to GT amount.

params._governanceToken: : address - The token that needs to be sent
params._tsryAmount: : uint256 - Amount of TSRY to be converted to amount of GT
params._tsryPrice: : uint256 - TESTING ONLY sets price of TSRY
params._user: : address - user address needed to find if the proxy is valid in the registry

getGTPrice(address).details: Gets price from oracle for GT (i.e., Aave/dollars).

getGTamount(uint256,address).details: Calculates corresponding GT from amount of TSRY given.

params._governanceToken: : address - GT needed to get price of
params._usdAmountTsry: : uint256 - Total value in USD (wei) of TSRY given.

getUserGTAllowance(uint256,address,uint2.details: Returns amount of GT from amount of TSRY (and price). Converts TSRY amount --> GT amount

params._token: : address - which token to get allowance for
params._tsryAmount: : uint256 - Amount of tsry to covert to GT

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

stakeToEarn(uint256,address).details: Allows user to stake GT in return for TSRY

params._amount: : uint - Amount of GT they want to stake
params._token: : address - The address of the GT

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

treasuryValue(uint256,uint256).details: Testing Only. Calculates value of TSRY given a set price and amount.

params._tsryPrice: : uint256 - Price in dollars / token (not given as dollars/wei hence * 1e18)
